executionArgs.additionalInstruction: Run comprehensive tests covering bugs, performance bottlenecks, security vulnerabilities, accessibility issues, SEO compliance, and cross-browser compatibility based on the PRD specifications. Focus on: 1) Functional correctness of all landing page sections 2) WCAG 2.1 AA accessibility compliance 3) Core Web Vitals (LCP ≤ 2.5s, CLS ≤ 0.1, INP ≤ 200ms) 4) Security best practices for external links and form validation 5) SEO meta tags and heading structure 6) Responsive design across mobile/tablet/desktop
